name: LET'S FLY HIGHER
description:
"Somebody help me!
I just want to fly higher?
But why are those people beating me?
is there something wrong with me?"
Said someone whose dream had to end in suicide because of being a victim of bullying.
If you don't like something about someone, you can say it nicely or ignore it.
Don't have to throw stones at him.
Are you a god so that the world can run as you wish? No!
How do we stop it? As Michael Jackson said,
"There are people dying. If you care enough for the living, make a better place for you and for me.”
Let's make it happen.

5000 X 5000 px
